      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "During the Soviet era, the city developed into a major centre for the production of ferrous and non-ferrous metallurgy, glass, iron, zinc, steel, chemical, and construction industries, as well as an important transit railway junction.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kostiantynivka",
      "source_type": "reference_work",
      "confidence_tier": "reported",
      "fact_id": "fct_002",
      "first_reported": "2026-07-08",
      "last_updated": "2026-07-08",
      "supersedes": null,
      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "It was the administrative center of the Kostiantynivka Raion until 2020, although it did not belong to it.",
